Angular production:
https://angular.io/guide/deployment
Angular run production locally to make sure it works.
>ng serve –prod
Or in our case:
>ng serve – prod –disable-host-check –host lvh.me –port 9000
TWO dashes

Create the files needed for production
>ng build –prod
TWO dashes
The output folder is:
ProjectFolder/dist/project_name
If you want to chang the output path, you can change the
outputPath property in the angular.json file.
